## Product

Our [organization](org-chart) delivers a [product](https://gratipay.com/) to
help companies and others pay for open source, in order to
[evolve](/big-picture/strategy) open organizations. &#x1f4b8; &#x1f4b8;
&#x1f4b8; &#x1f483;

Our current epic is &ldquo;[Make it easier for companies to fund open
source](https://github.com/gratipay/inside.gratipay.com/issues/987).&rdquo;


